李秉宪透露，《乌贼游戏》原计划只有一季https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-one-season-only-lee-byung-hun-3477415?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=squid-game-one-season-only-lee-秉勋Puah ZiweiThu, 03 Aug 2023 03:29:03 +0000 NewsTV NewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3477415 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乌贼游戏李秉宪" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “从无到有，创造出有的东西，就是这样”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-one-season-only-lee-byung-hun-3477415">李秉宪透露，《鱿鱼游戏》原计划只有一季，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乌贼游戏李秉宪" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/squid-game-lee-byung-hun-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/squid-game"><em>《鱿鱼游戏》</em></a>演员李秉宪透露，这部热门 Netflix 韩剧原计划只有一季。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/d-p-season-two-review-netflix-k-drama-3477043">《DP》第二季评论：一部令人痛心、沉重的续集</a></strong></li></ul><p>在该剧第一季中扮演主唱的李最近向韩国媒体谈到了即将推出的<em>《鱿鱼游戏》</em>第二季。在采访中，这位演员透露，系列导演黄东赫告诉他， <em>《乌贼游戏》</em>从未计划过第二季。</p><p> “自从我之前与<em>《乌贼游戏》</em>导演黄东赫合作过一部电影以来，我们彼此关系非常密切，”李在接受<a href="https://sbsstar.net/article/N1007294121/lee-byung-hun-says-squid-game-director-created-something-out-of-nothing-for-season-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>SBS Star</em></a>采访时说道，并补充说黄东赫“最初从未计划过表明有续集”。</p><p> “ <em>《鱿鱼游戏》</em>结束后，我们出去吃晚饭。晚餐时，我问他制作一个系列剧感觉如何。他说，‘由于压力，我掉了六颗牙齿。我再也不会做电视节目了，”李继续说道。 “But it was the show&#39;s global success that got him to make a sequel.”</p><p> Lee later spoke about the script for season two of <em>Squid Game</em> , saying that it made him feel like Hwang is a “true storyteller” and a “genius”. He added: “Creating something out of nothing, that&#39;s what it was. <em>Squid Game</em> was a show that originally wasn&#39;t intended to have a second season, so the script amazed me even more.”</p><p> In the down time between the first and second seasons of <em>Squid Game</em> , fans have come up with theories about the possible plot of the sequel. However, according to Lee, no one has come close to what the storyline will be: “I&#39;ve read lots of speculative articles, but none of them were even near the actual plot.”</p><p> In June, Netflix revealed <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-season-two-cast-3463267">the new cast for <em>Squid Game</em> season two</a> . It&#39;ll feature former <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/big-bang">Big Bang</a> member <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/t-o-p">TOP</a> , ex- <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/izone">IZ*ONE</a> singer <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jo-yu-ri">Jo Yu-ri</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/heartbeat"><em>Heartbeat</em></a> &#39;s Won Ji-an and <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-glory"><em>The Glory</em></a> &#39;s Park Sung-hoon, among others. They will be joined by returning cast members Lee Jung-Jae, Lee Byung-Hun, Wi Ha-Jun and Gong Yoo.</p><p> Netflix also previously unveiled <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-the-challenge-premiere-date-netflix-3444983">a first look at</a> <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-the-challenge-premiere-date-netflix-3444983">Squid Game: The Challenge</a> ,</em> the upcoming reality TV show based on the scripted K-drama series. The show will feature contestants competing for a cash prize of $4.56million (£3.65million) in a series of games inspired by the show – without the violent stakes.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/squid-game-one-season-only-lee-byung-hun-3477415">&#39;Squid Game&#39; was originally planned to have only one season, Lee Byung-hun reveals</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
